    "title": "Supply Chain Manager - Pickrr - Top MNC",
    "description": "Grow your career with Pickrr! We are hiring a Supply Chain Manager for our Ghaziabad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Pickrr:\nPickrr is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Pickrr!",
